Package: accessrmd
Title: Functions to Improve the Accessibility of Rmarkdown Documents
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Rich",
           family = "Leyshon",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "richard.leyshon@ons.gov.uk"),
           person(family = "datasciencecampus", role = "cph")
           )
Description: Provides a simple method to improve the accessibility of Rmarkdown
    documents. The package provides functions for creating or modifying
    Rmarkdown documents, resolving known errors and alerts that result in
    accessibility issues for screen reader users.
License: file LICENSE
